headline: Jack Henry (JKHY): Reassessing Valuation After Recent Share Price Strength
summary: Recent Performance and Market Context Jack Henry & Associates (JKHY) has quietly put together a strong run, with the stock up roughly 13% over the past month and about 12% in the past 3 months, handily beating broader market gains. See our latest analysis for Jack Henry & Associates. Zooming out, Jack Henry & Associates has seen its 1 year total shareholder return of 6.44% trail the recent 30 day share price return. This suggests momentum has picked up as investors warm to its steady fintech...
